printer_notes.3.0.0:
Don't remove the following keywords! These keywords are used in the "compatible printer" condition of the print and filament profiles to link the particular print and filament profiles to this printer profile.
PRINTER_VENDOR_LNL3D
PRINTER_MODEL_LNL3D_D3_VULCAN
PRINTER_HAS_ULTRADETAIL
PRINTER_HAS_HIGHSPEED
PRINTER_HAS_SUPERSPEED

start_gcode.3.0.0:
G21                                        ; Metric values
G90                                        ; Absolute positioning
M82                                        ; Set extruder to absolute mode
M107                                       ; Start with the fan off
G28                                        ; Move to min endstops
G92 E0                                     ; Reset extruder
G1 Z15.0 F3000                             ; Move the header up 15mm
M117 Final warmup                          ; LCD message
M140 S[first_layer_bed_temperature]        ; Set bed temp
M190 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0] - 5} ; Wait for bed temp-5
M104 S[first_layer_temperature]            ; Heat extruder rest of the way after heatbed
M109 S[first_layer_temperature]            ; Wait for extruder temp
G1 X40 Y5 Z4 F5000.0                       ; Move to position to prevent hitting clamps or bed
G1 X50 Y5 Z0.3 F5000.0                     ; Move to start position
G1 X110 Y5 Z0.3 F1500.0 E15                ; First purge line
G1 X70 Y5 Z0.3 F1500.0 E8                  ; Second pass
M117 Printing...                           ; LCD message

end_gcode.3.0.0:
M104 T0 S0                   ;left extruder heater off
M104 T1 S0                   ;right extruder heater off
M140 S0                      ;heated bed heater off (if you have it)
G91                          ;relative positioning
G1 E-1 F300                  ;retract the filament a bit before lifting the nozzle, to release some of the pressure
G1 Z+0.5 E-5 X-20 Y-20 F9000 ;move Z up a bit and retract filament even more
G28 X0 Y0                    ;move X/Y to min endstops, so the head is out of the way
M84                          ;steppers off
G90                          ;absolute positioning
